# Cairo 1.18.4 records length-bounded Pango glyph text without a trailing NUL.
# ASan's strict strndup interceptor reports the resulting one-byte read in the
# SDK library. Keep strict string checks enabled for Pinpoint and suppress only
# calls passing through Cairo's glyph-subsetting function.
interceptor_via_fun:_cairo_scaled_font_subsets_map_glyph
